"  - Passez au fournisseur 'custom-openai' pour les points de terminaison personnalisés."

#: internal/cli/helpers.go:447
msgid ""
"provider 'openai' requires authentication\n"
"\n"
"Option 1: Login interactively:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai\n"
"\n"
"Option 2: Choose a specific method:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --auth-method oauth\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --auth-method device\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --auth-method api-key\n"
"\n"
"Option 3: Pass key directly:\n"
"  --api-key YOUR_KEY or export OPENAI_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY\n"
"\n"
"Get an API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys"
msgstr ""
"le fournisseur 'openai' nécessite une authentification\n"
"\n"
"Option 1 : Se connecter de manière interactive :\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai\n"
"\n"
"Option 2 : Choisir une méthode spécifique :\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --auth-method oauth\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --auth-method device\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider openai --auth-method api-key\n"
"\n"
"Option 3 : Passer la clé directement :\n"
"  --api-key YOUR_KEY ou export OPENAI_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY\n"
"\n"
"Obtenez une clé API ici : https://platform.openai.com/api-keys"

#: internal/cli/helpers.go:460
